                <mxCell id="princBox" value="&lt;b&gt;Key principles&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Skills are versioned, composable units — agents compose, not duplicate&lt;br&gt;2. Any agent can invoke any skill it has been granted via RBAC policy&lt;br&gt;3. New skills added without redeploying agents — hot-pluggable registry&lt;br&gt;4. Human approval gates on high-risk skill invocations" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#F4F6FB;strokeColor=#8A94A6;strokeWidth=0.5;fontSize=11;fontColor=#3D4663;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=5;" parent="1" vertex="1">
