                <mxCell id="tkhYth2j_04fy7iLB3qD-57" value="&lt;b&gt;AKS deployment considerations&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• HPA: engineer-pod scales 1→4 on CPU/queue depth; others fixed at 1–2 replicas&lt;br&gt;• Node pools: system (orchestration) · worker (agents) · gpu (LLM if self-hosted)&lt;br&gt;• Network policy: agent-workers → tool-adapters (allow) · agent-workers ↔ internet (deny)&lt;br&gt;• Pod identity: Azure Workload Identity per namespace for least-privilege AAD access&lt;br&gt;• Skill updates: Rolling update on skill-registry; agents hot-reload via gRPC stream" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=3;dashed=1;dashPattern=6 4;fillColor=#F4F6FB;strokeColor=#8A94A6;fontSize=11;fontColor=#3D4663;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=5;strokeWidth=0.5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="75" y="1300" width="1025" height="140" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
